                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Pōkar Nikaṇṭu</title>, that is, the "Thesaurus of Pōkar", a Siddha medical work by Pōkar. See Zvelebil (1995, p. 566, s.v. Pōkar).</p>
